Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Time for more taxes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440lhc
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 30 Oct 1987
The money men are waiting for President Reagan to take the lead in attempts to stabilise the rocky economy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less